To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private ThreeInside _threeinside;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_threeinside = ThreeInside(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_threeinside.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "threeinside", _threeinside.Current.Value);
}
